values:
<lj user="hokkaido_hick">

I just found my roommate now!

They haven't said anything to me yet, though...I think I finally know who they are!

...

Maybe...

Well...I'm having a nice conversation with Gaara...

somehow we're getting along pretty well

...

I checked out my room...

BORING

You know...I'm just gonna use my backup weapons!

...

Okay, so I lied. I did bring some weapons ^^;

But can you blame me? I knew something weird would start going on eventually!

I'm gonna cover the walls with kunai, katana, shuriken, swords, EVERYTHING I CAN FIND!

YEAH!

*hyped up now*

I don't know why, but I feel really happy today! I mean...meeting my new roommate, I still have to do. Tampopo was it? I need to check on that. 

(( Seriously, I do ))

I'm just seriously all hyped up about this competition!

...

*sigh*

The only problem is I didn't bring any weapons with me...I figured I wouldn't need them...

omg

WHY THE HELL DID I THINK THAT?!?!

I always need my weapons!

You never know when the enemy is gonna attack!

...

Well...I have to go now!

(( I have to go to my birthday party splee ^^ ))
